    "message": "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #1f2933;\">\n<h3>Visitor No-Show</h3>\n<p>The following visitor was approved for today but did not check in.</p>\n\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 12px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f4f5f7;\"><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Visitor</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.visitor_full_name }}</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Company</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.company__organisation or 'N/A' }}</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f4f5f7;\"><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Expected Date</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.visit_date }}</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Expected Time</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.expected_checkin }} - {{ doc.expected_checkout }}</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f4f5f7;\"><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Purpose</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.purpose_of_visit }}</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Contact Phone</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.mobile_number or 'N/A' }}</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f4f5f7;\"><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><b>Contact Email</b></td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{ doc.email_id or 'N/A' }}</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p>If needed, please follow up with the visitor or cancel the pass.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 16px;\"><a href=\"{{ frappe.utils.get_url() }}/app/visitor-pass/{{ doc.name }}\">View Pass</a></p>\n</div>",
